#HELPS

0 USE~
Syntax: use <object name>
        use <object name> <target>

The use command is a shortcut command that allows you to interact with a wide 
variety of objects.  You can still quaff a potion, but you can also use 
the 'use' command.  You can still zap with a wand, but you can also use the 
'use' command to zap (this command is slightly more verbose but it allows you 
to use a wide variety of items without having to remember the individual command 
for each item type).

~

0 PKILL PKILLING PKILLER 'PLAYER KILLING' PSTEAL PSTEALING 'PLAYER STEALING'~
Player killing and player stealing are allowed to all clan members
(including loners), provided the victim is is within 8 levels of the
character and is also in a clan.  This will flag you as a "WANTED", allowing 
any character to attack, and also provoking action from the city guard.
~

